| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4678 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 85d1eecc-f427-5c8b-a6b3-e0c3c9666449"
